roll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">18.1k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">Apache-2.0</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">coze-studio 是一个集成化的 AI 代理开发平台，提供全方位的可视化工具，简化了 AI 代理的创建、调试和部署流程。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持最新大型模型及多种开发模式与框架，打造便捷高效的 AI 代理开发环境</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供包括提示词（prompt）、检索增强生成（RAG）、插件、工作流等核心技术支持</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">内置完整应用模板和构建框架，实现低成本快速构建多样 AI 代理及业务逻辑定制</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于微服务架构与领域驱动设计原则，高性能、高扩展性且易定制的后端框架</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端采用 React + TypeScript 实现，可通过无代码或低代码方式进行视觉设计和调试</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持模型管理、多资源管理（插件、知识库、数据库等）以及开放 API 和 SDK 集成能力</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">EvolutionAPI/evolution-api</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/EvolutionAPI/evolution-api\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/EvolutionAPI/evolution-api</a></span></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">6.0k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">NOASSERTION</span></code></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">evolution-api 是一个开源的多平台消息集成 API，最初基于 Baileys 库实现 WhatsApp 控制功能，现已扩展支持包括官方 WhatsApp Business API、Typebot、Chatwoot、Dify 和 OpenAI 等多种服务。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1rem;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:8px;margin-right:0px;padding-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持基于 Baileys 的免费 WhatsApp Web API 和 Meta 官方的云端 WhatsApp Business API 两种连接方式</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供丰富的第三方集成，如构建对话机器人（Typebot）、客户服务系统（Chatwoot）、消息队列事件接收（RabbitMQ、Amazon SQS）及 AI 能力扩展（OpenAI）</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">具备轻量级版本 Evolution API Lite，适合微服务环境下高效简洁使用</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持媒体文件存储到 Amazon S3 或 Minio，提高数据管理灵活性</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">实施非敏感数据遥测以优化产品性能与用户体验</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">jwohlwend/boltz</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/jwohlwend/boltz\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/jwohlwend/boltz</a></span></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 2px;margin-right: 2px;padding-top: 2px;padding-bottom: 2px;padding-left: 4px;padding-right: 4px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">3.4k</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; License:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spacing: 0em;background-attachment: scroll;b